com.skobbler.ngx.versioning

Interface SKMapUpdateListener


  • public interface SKMapUpdateListener
    The SKMapUpdateListener is used to receive callbacks related to map versioning.
    Version:
    2.4

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onMapVersionSet(int newVersion)
      Notifies when the map version is set to the library.This method is notified on the UI thread.
      void onNewVersionDetected(int newVersion)
      Notifies when a new version for the map is detected.This method is notified on the UI thread.
      void onNoNewVersionDetected()
      Notifies when there's no new map version detected.This method is notified on the UI thread.
      void onVersionFileDownloadTimeout()
      Notifies when there was a timeout in downloading the version file.This method is notified on the UI thread.
